**you may be muted/banned for breaking any of the below rules at the admins discretion**

:small_orange_diamond: Don't be mean/condescending/racist/homophobic, use common sense

:small_orange_diamond: No NSFW content

:small_orange_diamond: Try to stay on topic in the appropriate channel

:small_orange_diamond: English only except for in international channels

:small_orange_diamond: Use spoiler tags on new content (movies/shows/games/etc.)

:small_orange_diamond: Trading outside of games with anyone in this discord is at your own risk

・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・

Check out #bio to get familiarized with some of the awesome people you will be playing with :peepoLove:
And of course, if you wish, add your own bio and pic :hypers:

・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・

Set Discord roles over at #roles

・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・

Contact the admins by using the !contact command. This can only be done by private messaging the bot, @Rubybot.

Use this for submitting complaints, private suggestions, requests for new ingame ranks/rights that you qualify for, or anything else you wish to contact us privately about :hypers: 

*the message will be sent to a private channel visible only to @Owner, @Leader, @SiC, @Trustee, and @Protector*

